{"tid":661436,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[用電話挖虛擬貨幣] Sweatcoin","createTime":"2018-05-11T14:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T01:48:11.000Z","uid":48234,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7a2c0753f3822d6f2567a3490e228824f088fcba","tid":661436,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T14:23:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Sweatcoin 跑步賺虛擬貨幣　盤據美國排行榜首</span><br />\n<br />\n跑步也可以賺錢？近日，英國團隊開發出一款名叫「Sweatcoin」的應用程式。記錄用家的運動情況，並按此向用家支付虛擬貨幣，可說是最「健康」的賺錢方法。 Sweatcoin 運用區塊鏈技術，當用家跑了 1,000步，就能獲得相等約 0.95 個 Sweatcoin 虛擬貨幣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-01-17-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%888.35.25-694x417.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2018-01-17-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25888.35.25-694x417.png&h=18cd22b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個應用程式在美國地區大受歡迎，更盤據免費排行榜榜首，證明以金錢鼓勵人們運動的確十分有效。當應用程式記錄用家跑了 1,000 步時，就會向用家支付約值相等於約 5 美分的 Sweatcoin。而為確保數據的真實性， Sweatcoin 更採用了區塊鏈技術，令黑客難以改動數據。另外，應用程式會比對手機的 GPS 和步數資料，防止用家以搖手機等方式作弊，確保每一個 Sweatcoin  都是辛苦運動而來。<br />\n<br />\n而用家所獲得的 Sweatcoin ，可在應用程式中兌換不同的服務和商品，同時亦可轉給其他用戶，或作慈善捐贈，但開發團隊的野心並不止於此。創辦人 Oleg Fomenko 曾於訪問時表示，最終希望能將 Sweatcoin 的匯率與英鎊掛鉤，成為一個穩定的虛擬貨幣。但可惜 Sweatcoin 目前只開放給英美及愛爾蘭地區用戶使用，香港用家要多等一下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F2-4.png&h=9bcf62d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F2-4.png&h=9bcf62d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F2-4.png&h=9bcf62d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1-35-694x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F1-35-694x390.jpg&h=2aba0b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/01/18/sweat-coin/software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2Fsweat-coin%2Fsoftware%2F&d=79svys0VV8dejz5Takm7EAIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=ed784188\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/01/18/sweat-coin/software/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sweatco.in/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsweatco.in%2F&d=79svys0VV8dejz5Takm7EAIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=144194fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://sweatco.in/</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">幾時先輪到香港有呀?屌你老母好撚正呀喂</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58cd7fd2d4fcb9df438e03c1ede99ded095f3ad","tid":661436,"uid":124107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T10:11:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc8d301c3997dd120eb4f063a644bd1a5102bb2b","tid":661436,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T10:28:36.000Z","msg":"幾正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805b4d12e0c6e71cb35f44a3a27c60fca682d21c","tid":661436,"uid":90017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T10:31:59.000Z","msg":"黎到香港會變左開CHEAT大賽"},{"pid":"e21a369e76f1285a0f8db6c6b659dc914bcb2f8a","tid":661436,"uid":55701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T10:35:30.000Z","msg":"搭地鐵成班人chok手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class